# Specific to Android

- Use the UDF or USF architecture pattern for creating new ViewModels refer to [mvi-usf.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/mvi-usf.mdc)
- Don't use xml and fragmenents when possible. Prefer Jetpack Compose UI
- Use repository pattern for data persistence